
Mind mapping is a useful strategic tool.
With a mind map, you can plan the projects, strategies and goals. 
Futhure, mind maps are a fantastic tool to collaborate while sharing and working in teams.
Benefits of mind mapping are: High efficiency, valuable overview of a central concept , simple, fast and fun.
To continuously improve our strategic thinking skills, we should:
. Observe
. Reflect
. Ask questions creatively
. COnsider the whole picture
. Propose solutions based on understanding
